{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e610dbfaef","title":"毛泽东对北京卫戍区关于在大、中学开展军训的两个总结报告的两条批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6f8eef5264","index":0,"year":1967,"month":2,"day":19,"articleId":"e610dbfaef"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"21964ca7d5","type":"title","text":"对北京卫戍区关于在大、中学开展军训的两个总结报告的两条批语","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e610dbfaef"},{"id":"81a0a7c344","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e610dbfaef"},{"id":"4e09de5100","type":"appellation","text":"林彪同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e610dbfaef"},{"id":"ca259aea2f","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）此两件应即转发全国。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e610dbfaef"},{"id":"996387b7a6","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）大学中学和小学高年级每年训练一次，每次二十天。上课以后，在军训的二十天中，军训时间每天不要超过四小时，同时学校原课程每天相应减少时间四小时。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e610dbfaef"},{"id":"182ad9a52a","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）党、政、军、民机关，除老年外，中年青年都要实行军训，每年二十天。以上请酌办。都不要发表。各地经验已超过北京。我的批语也有些不适应新情况。因此都不宜发表。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e610dbfaef"}],"page":{"id":"a6038ddfbb","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e610dbfaef","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}